preambule.al:
Considering that the forces of one State Party to the present
            Agreement may be sent and received, by separate arrangement, into
            the territory of another State Party;

li.al:
``Party/Parties to the North Atlantic Treaty" referred
                  to in the applicable documents, means the States Parties to the
                  present Agreement;

``North Atlantic Treaty area" referred to in the
                  applicable documents, means the territories of the States
                  Parties to the present Agreement;
